oken punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>props <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> props<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// ...</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Ve bu dÃ¼ÅŸÃ¼nce doÄŸruya Ã§ok da uzak deÄŸil â€” gerÃ§ekten de <a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/react/blob/1d25aa5787d4e19704c049c3cfa985d3b5190e0d/packages/react/src/ReactBaseClasses.js#L22\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Ã¶yle yapÄ±yor</a>.</p>\n<p>Ama nedense, <code class=\"language-text\">super()</code> fonksiyonunu <code class=\"language-text\">props</code> gÃ¶ndermeden Ã§aÄŸÄ±rsanÄ±z bile, <code class=\"language-text\">render</code> ve diper metodlarÄ±n iÃ§inden <code class=\"language-text\">this.props</code>â€˜a eriÅŸebiliyorsunuz. (Ä°nanmÄ±yorsanÄ±z kendiniz deneyebilirsiniz!)</p>\n<p>Peki <em>bu</em> nasÄ±l Ã§alÄ±ÅŸÄ±yor? MeÄŸerse <strong>React <em>sizin</em> constructor fonksiyonunuzdan hemen sonra, <code class=\"language-text\">props</code> parametresini kendi atÄ±yor:</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\">  <span class=\"token comment\">// React'Ä±n iÃ§i</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> instance <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">YourComponent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>props<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  instance<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>props <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> props<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Bu nedenle <code class=\"language-text\">super()</code> iÃ§ine <code class=\"language-text\">props</code> gÃ¶ndermeyi unutsanÄ±z bile, React yine de sonradan onu tanÄ±mlayacak. Bunun bir sebebi var.</p>\n<p>React classâ€™lar iÃ§in destek saÄŸladÄ±ÄŸÄ± sÄ±rada, sadece ES6 classâ€™larÄ± iÃ§in destek eklemedi. AmaÃ§, olabildiÄŸince geniÅŸ alanda class yapÄ±larÄ±nÄ± desteklemekti. O zamanlar ClojureScript, CoffeeScript, ES6, Fable, Scala.js, TypeScript, veya diÄŸer Ã§Ã¶zÃ¼mlerin component tanÄ±mlamada ne kadar baÅŸarÄ±lÄ± olacaklarÄ± <a href=\"https://reactjs.org/blog/2015/01/27/react-v0.13.0-beta-1.html#other-languages\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">kesin deÄŸildi</a>. Yani React kasÄ±tlÄ± olarak <code class=\"language-text\">super()</code> fonksiyonunun zorunlu olmasÄ±nda tarafsÄ±z kaldÄ± - ES6 zorunlu kÄ±lsa da.</p>\n<p>Peki bu <code class=\"language-text\">super(props)</code> yerine sadece <code class=\"language-text\">super()</code> yazabileceÄŸiniz anlamÄ±na mÄ± geliyor?</p>\n<p><strong>BÃ¼yÃ¼k ihtimalle hayÄ±r Ã§Ã¼nkÃ¼ hala biraz kafa karÄ±ÅŸtÄ±rÄ±cÄ±.</strong> Tabi ki, React zaten <code class=\"language-text\">this.props</code> deÄŸerini sizin constructorâ€™Ä±nÄ±z Ã§alÄ±ÅŸtÄ±ktan <em>sonra</em> atayacaktÄ±r. Ancak <code class=\"language-text\">this.props</code> deÄŸeri, <code class=\"language-text\">super</code> fonksiyonunu Ã§aÄŸÄ±rma satÄ±rÄ± ve constructorâ€™Ä±nÄ±zÄ±n sonu <em>arasÄ±nda</em> tanÄ±mlanmamÄ±ÅŸ olacaktÄ±r.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight has-highlighted-lines\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token comment\">// React'Ä±n iÃ§i</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Component</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">constructor</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">props</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\